				</ul>
				<ul class="mui-table-view font12">
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell">
						运费: ¥<font freight>20.00</font>
					</li>
					<li class="mui-table-view-cell">
						<span class="color">
							<strong>合计: ¥<font class="all-price-ele" min="600"></font></strong>
						</span>
						<p class="font12">运费: ¥20.00</font></p>
						<a class="mui-btn main-color FFF font12" href="post-order.html">
							提交订单
